last_episode_to_air.name: The Lucky Country
last_episode_to_air.overview: On the final leg of her journey, Miriam hitches a ride to one of the most isolated parts of the country, the Gulf of Carpentaria, to see where the wealth of the Lucky Country comes from.

name: Miriam Margolyes: Almost Australian
overview: A revealing documentary series; following celebrated film and television star Miriam Margolyes as she embarks on an epic two-month journey across the nation to discover what it means to be Australian today.
